      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASH CRUISE (1) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (25.52) last time in a Grade 4/5 at Q Lakeside. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Can atone. ROLLING IN MUD (5) placed last time (25.30) at this track in a NG, finishing second and beaten 1.75 lengths. Already a winner from this draw. Looks one of the chances. GO WILD BLUE (8) has a strong winning strike-rate over this journey with two wins and a placing from four tries. Missed the frame latest (30.29) when fourth over 520m at Q Parklands in a OPEN. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. ON THE WHISPER (7) was out of placings last time (20.07) at Capalaba in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 3.5 lengths. Has already won two times from this draw.",
